Package de.dlr.proseo.storagemgr.s3

Class S3Configuration

java.lang.Object
de.dlr.proseo.storagemgr.s3.S3Configuration
public class S3Configuration extends Object
Holds the configuration settings required to connect to and interact with an S3 storage system. It allows for the customization of various aspects such as access credentials, region, bucket, paths, and behavior-related settings like request attempts and file transfer management.
Author:
Denys Chaykovskiy
